    <item>
      <title>Altice France 将媒体出售所得现金移出债权人控制范围</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/altice-france-moves-media-sale-cash-out-of-creditors-reach</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Altice France 将近期资产剥离的部分收益转移至债权人无法触及的范围内，该公司正准备就削减 240 亿欧元（262 亿美元）债务展开讨论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/altice-france-moves-media-sale-cash-out-of-creditors-reach</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 18:34:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>AT&T 数据泄露事件引发 FCC 调查，引发广泛安全担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/at-t-says-new-hack-includes-records-of-customer-calls-texts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国电话电报公司 (AT&amp;T) 周五表示，黑客窃取了长达六个月的手机客户数据缓存，首次披露了威胁国家安全的大规模网络安全漏洞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/at-t-says-new-hack-includes-records-of-customer-calls-texts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 10:26:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
